{"div":{"@xmlns":"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0","@type":"article","@xml:id":"MG-1682-09b_010","head":{"value":"Eglogue","id":"/div/head"},"bibl":{"title":{"value":"Mercure galant","id":"/div/bibl/title"},"#":{"value":", septembre 1682 (seconde partie) [tome 10], p. 10-15.","id":"/div/bibl/#"}},"p":[{},"Je n’attendray point que vous m’ayez fait connoistre le plaisir que vous aura infailliblement causé la lecture de l’Idille de Madame des Houlieres, employé dans la premiere Partie de cette Lettre, pour vous envoyer un autre Ouvrage de cette illustre Personne. En voicy un Pastoral, dont les Vers aisez, doux &amp; naturels, vous feront admirer de plus en plus la beauté de son Génie."],"quote":{"label":{"value":"EGLOGUE.","id":"/div/quote/label"},"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Assise au bord de la Seine","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Sur le panchant d’un Costeau,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"La Bergere Célimene","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Laisse paistre son Troupeau.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il descend dans la Prairie","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Sans qu’elle daigne songer","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que le Loup pourra manger","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Sa Brebis la plus chérie.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Le souvenir d’un Berger","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que la Fortune cruelle","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[9]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Force à vivre éloigné d’elle","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[10]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dans un Climat Etranger,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[11]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Cause la langueur mortelle","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[12]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui luy fait tout négliger.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[13]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tantost cedant à la force","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[14]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De ses amoureux transports,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[15]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Elle grave sur l’écorce","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[16]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Des Arbrisseaux de ces bords,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[17]/#"}},"Puisse durer, puisse croistre","L’ardeur de mon jeune Amant,","Comme feront sur ce Hestre","Ces marques de mon tourment !",{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tantost meslant sur le sable","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[22]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Le nom d’Acante &amp; le sien,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[23]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Elle trouve insuportable","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[24]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qu’un Zéphir impitoyable","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[25]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"En passant n’en laisse rien.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[26]/#"}},"Quelle cruelle avanture,",{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dit-elle avec un soûpir,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[28]/#"}},"Si ce qu’a fait le Zéphir","M’est un veritable augure,","Que de si tendres amours,","Ne dureront pas toûjours !","Je briserois ma Musete","S’il estoit un Imposteur,","Et du fer de ma Houlete","Je me percerois le cœur.",{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"A ces mots, elle repasse","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[37]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dans son esprit alarmé,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[38]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"L’air, les traits, l’esprit, la grace","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[39]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De ce Berger trop aimé.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[40]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Les Oyseaux de ce Bocage","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[41]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Se taisent pour écouter","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[42]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ce qu’ils l’entendent chanter","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[43]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Du beau Berger qui l’engage.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[44]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ils voudroient le répeter,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[45]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mais leur plus tendre ramage","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[46]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ne la sçauroit imiter.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[47]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Jamais cette triste Amante","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[48]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ne voit sur l’herbe naissante","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[49]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Folastrer d’heureux Amans,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[50]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qu’elle ne se représente","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[51]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Combien l’absence d’Acante","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[52]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Luy couste de doux momens.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[53]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Jamais des Bergers ne viennent","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[54]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De ces bords délicieux","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[55]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Où ses destins le retiennent,","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[56]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que son amour curieux","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[57]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ne s’informe si ces Lieux","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[58]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ont des Nymphes assez belles","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[59]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pour faire des Infidelles.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[60]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Enfin mille fois le jour","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[61]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Elle veut, elle apprehende","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[62]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tout ce que craint &amp; demande","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[63]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Le plus violent amour.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[64]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Qu’on doit plaindre une Bergere","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[65]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Si facile à s’alarmer !","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[66]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pourquoy du plaisir d’aimer","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[67]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Faut-il se faire une affaire ?","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[68]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Quels Bergers en font autant","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[69]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dans l’heureux siecle où nous sommes ?","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[70]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Acante qu’elle aime tant","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[71]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Est sans-doute un Inconstant","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[72]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Comme tous les autres Hommes.","id":"/div/quote/lg/l[73]/#"}}]}}}}